data.description: Step into this inviting home with updates throughout! The freshly painted kitchen cabinetry adds a crisp, clean look with stainless steel appliances. The bright and airry living room has a brick fireplace and leads directly to the large screened in porch. The updated laminate flooring upstairs add a modern touch to the space. Enjoy the serene outdoors with the screened-in porch,  deck and raised garden beds!  The primary bedroom's vaulted ceiling adds an airy feel to the space. With new paint throughout and updated light fixtures and bathroom fixtures, this home is a delightful blend of style and comfort. Voluntary HOA only! Don't miss the workshop area underneath the deck.
